{"tid":698772,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"同老豆食飯有感上一輩思想的問題","createTime":"2018-06-12T04:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T06:17:15.000Z","uid":11293,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92d45e1096be21262343d6494d018ee4a1e5e6c0","tid":698772,"uid":11293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日同老豆落茶記食飯<br />\n嗰陣9點，埋到位我老豆想叫個扒餐<br />\n但你地都明，去到8幾點9點，旺嘅茶記有啲野賣晒無貨都合理吖<br />\n<br />\n伙記：燕麥飯同意粉都賣晒，得番白飯<br />\n老豆：咁你乜都無，係咪計番平我地？<br />\n<br />\n嗰下我真係想拍檯叫佢唔好咁，賣晒其他咪食白飯，幾十蚊個扒餐都要嘈嗰幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一輩嘅思想就係乜都要計盡，我地啲90後就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識得體諒同包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52132e205ce1c5c816c64854a192ecfdf27b8593","tid":698772,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"老豆：咁你乜都無，係咪計番平我地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個邏輯係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0287214bdb40a1fc621037a968e8ca0556dfe9f8","tid":698772,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52132e205ce1c5c816c64854a192ecfdf27b8593","tid":698772,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"老豆：咁你乜都無，係咪計番平我地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個邏輯係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"佢老豆意思應該係佢個餐係賠燕麥飯意粉，不過無曬，咁係唔係要平少少。類似譚仔少米線減一蚊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知道有無Get錯"},{"pid":"ff0cd7a8dba1d1ea55652f6f965de2776cb06700","tid":698772,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0287214bdb40a1fc621037a968e8ca0556dfe9f8","tid":6987